I want to thank me 😁
No matter what happens, what you’re doing, where you are, don’t forget to prioritize yourself. Take time to take care of yourself, do things that make you happy, and enjoy your life. 🍃

2022 has been a year full of self-improvement, changes, and adventures. Self-improvement through developing my own sense of self, becoming more independent, and learning the strength I have within myself. Changes occurred by morphing into a better version of myself, learning how to adapt myself in hard situations and times, and finding peace with myself and changing my circle to match my life goals. Finally, adventures by traveling to so many new and beautiful places, experiencing new and crazy situations, and learning about so many beautiful cultures. I crossed off so many of my bucket list destinations and I can’t wait to see what 2023 has in store for me.
You can’t separate peace from freedom because no one can be at peace unless he has his freedom🍃
Look at me habibi 😎

Accept what is, let go of what was, and have faith in what will be🍃___________________________________

My birthday wish come true. As always, April proved to be another beautiful month full of blessings. After so many years of working and praying for the place I would call home, the moment is finally here. For many, this may seem like an ordinary step in a persons life. But to me, this reminds me how grateful I am for the life I have lived and how important it is to be thankful for everything we have in our lives. So excited to start the new chapter of my life. Looking forward to making new and amazing memories in our home. Now that I’ve seen one dream come true, I know I need to keep challenging myself. This is only the first step to many future achievements.
